content:
Use predefined calculated insights in the Automotive data kit to view aggregated information about customer lifetime value, vehicle lifetime value, and customer satisfaction. Track the revenue from dealer sales, direct manufacturer sales, and sale of parts and accessories for each vehicle or customer. You can also track the count of all open cases and the count of open cases segmented by owner and vehicle.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions where Data Cloud and Automotive are enabled.

Users must have access to the objects and fields for the calculated insights included in the Automotive Data Kit bundle. In Data Cloud, on the Calculated Insights tab, go to the All list view. Select a record, such as Vehicle Lifetime Value or Count Of Open Cases By Owner.
title: Calculated Insights for Automotive
